Description:
Contemporary combined with Convenience!
LJ Hooker proudly presents this golden opportunity which is ideal for all first home buyers, downsizers and Astute investors looking to be nestled in a highly sought-after and central pocket of Dandenong. This well-maintained home is within a short distance to all amenities and provides the convenient and ideal lifestyle you have been searching for. To all the investors out there, this home is currently leased out to lovely tenants for $1390PCM on a month to month basis.
Offering 2 very good-sized bedrooms with BIR, master bedroom with access to the spacious balcony overlooking the lovely park and Dandenong Creek Trail, a spacious family area, second living zone, dining area adjacent to the delightful kitchen equipped with gas cooking and an abundance of cupboard space. The second balcony, main bathroom, separate toilet and laundry make up the interior of this lovely home.
Features of this home include: split system, electric wall heater, dishwasher, single lock-up garage and much more!
Located within a stones-throw away from Dandenong Station, Dandenong Plaza, Dandenong Market, multiple Pre-schools, Primary Schools and High Schools. Dandenong Bypass/Eastlink, Dandenong CBD, Dandenong Creek walking trail, public transport and recreational facilities. This home is all but ready for you to make it your own.
Do not miss out on this excellent opportunity!
Call Ben Jusufi or Burak Gul for any further information!
*PHOTO I.D. REQUIRED UPON INSPECTION*

GROUND FLOOR APARTMENT IN CENTRAL LOCATION
This beautifully presented 2 bedroom and ground floor apartment has it all. Spacious living area, sizeable bedrooms with built in robes, 1 good size bathroom, 1 separate toilet and updated kitchen with a space for dining table and gas cook top. At the back of the property there is a nice garden to relax when you are not at work plus 1 single lock up garage. Close to Dandenong station, Dandenong Plaza, Dandenong Market and local schools. Currently tenanted on month to month basis for $920 per calendar month. An inspection will impress!

Description:
NEST OR INVEST
This 5 year old modern townhouse is in pristine condition and will suit the most fastidious investor, first-home buyer or someone wishing to down size. It is located in a highly sought after pocket and within close distance to central Dandenong.
Downstairs consists of a spacious open plan lounge room with large kitchen adjacent to an undercover outdoor area plus guest's powder room. Upstairs boasts a spacious layout with two double bedrooms all serviced by a large central bathroom.
It is close to schools, yarraman and Dandenong stations, shops and has easy access to all amenities.
Features:
• 2 bedrooms - master with walk in robe
• Two way ensuite
• Split system reverse cycle heating & cooling
• Guest toilet + powder room
• Spacious kitchen with new gas appliances
• Meals and lounge area
• Single lock up garage with remote access
• Fitted rainwater tank for gardening & toilets
• Garden shed
• Low maintenance front & rear gardens
A quality home or investment for all buyers.

Description:
A very neat unit within walking distance of Dandenong Plaza
Literally within sight of Dandenong Plaza, this classically styled clinker brick unit is perfectly placed within walking distance of all that central Dandenong has to offer including shops, eateries, cinemas, parks and transport. Perfect for an investor or occupier, the home is in neat and largely original condition making it an ideal candidate for a cosmetic renovation. Features include a spacious lounge with bay window, gas heater and an air conditioner plus a neat kitchen with wall oven, gas cook top and an adjoining meals area. There are 2 bedrooms with built in wardrobes as well as a bathroom with a luxurious spa bath, a dual entry toilet and a full laundry. Outside there's a single garage and a north facing courtyard dominated by the expansive covered patio that is great for year 'round entertaining.
BE QUICK BEFORE YOU MISS OUT!!

FOR SALE
Phone Enquiry ID:48624
12 ETON COURT, DANDENONG, VIC 3175 $ 650 000 +
Turn-Key Ready to move in, or as Your Investment Property
This well-maintained brick veneer house on a 539 sqm corner block setting, has a magnificent 180° panoramic view overlooking the wetland parks, with Endeavour Hills, and the Dandenong Ranges in the distance. The secure backyard has a number of established fruit trees, with potentials for a vege garden, and chook house.
Features
• 3 Bedrooms, 1 Bathroom, 1 Toilet, Carport space for 2 cars
• Dwelling Area 93 sqm
• Walk through Lounge to Dining area
• Reverse Cycle Air Conditioner
• Polished Timber floorboards
• Venetian blinds
Established Conveniences
• 200 m walk for buses to Monash University, Chadstone, Dandenong Shops, Markets, and Train Station
• Walking distance to the milk bar, Dandenong Hospital, number of medical facilities, and Chisholm TAFE
• 15 min bike ride to primary and secondary schools, the Oasis Gym and Swimming Pool
• Adjoining Dandenong Bike Trail for your early morning jog, or a bike ride to the Basketball Stadium, or for a family picnic at the Wetlands Recreation Area, 20 mins. away.
Redevelopment Potentials
• Dual Occupancy, with individual street frontage

Description:
Location and Lifestyle
Calling families, first home owners, future planners and investors - this terrific townhouse ticks all the boxes for family living. Located walking distance to shops, schools, parks and public transport youâ??ll just love the location and lifestyle on offer here!
Set to impress from the beginning, the classic two storey facade, neatly landscaped gardens and secure front fence create instant kerbside appeal. Inside, the neutral interiors and versatile layout are finished with eye-catching details. The formal living room with its feature cathedral ceiling, grand arched window and dazzling pendant light is the perfect setting for entertaining family and friends. The separate kitchen and meals area are ideal for casual family living and enjoy a connection to the rear courtyard. The kitchen is fitted with stainless steel appliances; 4 burner gas cooktop, 600mm wide electric wall oven and dishwasher as well as a handy breakfast bar.
On offer are three bedrooms including not one but two master suites both with built in robes and direct ensuite access. With one positioned on each level the layout provides flexible living options ideal for guest accommodation and multi-generational living. Completing the first floor layout is the third bedroom with built in robe, a second living area with study nook and balcony access. Further comforts of the home include ducted heating, split system air conditioning, alarm system, security shutters and lavish curtains throughout.
This tidy package is complete with a low maintenance courtyard, water tank, pergola and single car garage with remote controlled door.
Add to the list of features a convenient location close to Dandenong West Primary School, Dandenong High School, Greaves Reserve, Dandenong Plaza and the iconic Dandenong Markets as well as easy transport options and close access to Eastlink and the Monash Freeway. An impressive must see property, call us today!

Description:
The ugly duckling is now a beautiful swan!
Sale By Set Date: Monday 11th December at 5pm (unless sold prior)
This outstanding opportunity conveniently located close to Dandenong Central, schools, recreational facilities, the Monash Freeway, as well as public transport, this lovely unit is ideal for downsizers, first home buyers or investors.
Until recently an ugly duckling, this unit has been magnificently transformed into a beautiful swan, complete with new paint, floor coverings, and spacious kitchen with fresh stainless steel appliances.
With the bedroom presenting in a roomy and airy feel, this is a unique possibility to purchase a single storey property in a small group of 4. You’ll be amazed at the transformation with the kitchen showing so much light and is now an inviting and welcoming home.
Outside the surprises keep coming with gorgeous outdoor tiles and surrounding mulch. Ideal for outside entertaining, this home is now a wonderful opportunity for all who enter. There’s even been improvements under the eave’s with new lighting and security.
Don’t miss out on this outstanding prospect!

Description:
PERFECT FOR A FIRST TIME INVESTOR WITH TENANT FOR THE NEXT YEAR MIN AND CASH FLOW OF $1536 PER CALENDAR MONTH. ALSO PERFECT FOR A FIRST HOME BUYER, DO
A superb lifestyle acquisition offering generous space, a delightful outlook and excellent location with almost brand new conditions! A huge appeal for those seeking a premium property or a first home, to downsize or invest!
A great opportunity exists to secure this home in the popular, acclaimed and convenient location of Metro Village. Ideal for a first time investor or couple looking for low maintenance living. A spacious 2 bedroom unit, both rooms with private access to the sun lit balcony. Featuring a huge hostess kitchen with expansive breakfast bar, plenty of cupboard space and quality stainless steel appliances. A high end bathroom with mosaics, fully tiled splash back and a custom made porcelain vanity basin.
You will love to entertain with the addition of the outdoor pergola suitable for special events or BBQ's with your family and friends. This overlooks a fully enclosed courtyard with enough room for the kids or pets to enjoy the morning sun! Car accommodation won't be an issue with the single electric garage with rear access or off street parking. A GREAT location with easy access to train stations, Dandenong's shopping precinct, 24 hour gym and plenty of well-known restaurants.
Previously leased for 350/w. Smart investors, start crunching your numbers, this one's a money maker! Call Zed now before it's too late!

Fabulous land with unlimited potential

Potential and results will only depend on your imagination. An opportunity that is not to be missed.
